                <p class="lead">Add your suggestions and interact with others to make a positive impact in your community.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="row row-cols-1 row-cols-md-2 g-4">
            <div class="col">
                <div class="d-flex">
                    <div class="flex-shrink-0">
                        <div class="d-flex align-items-center justify-content-center bg-primary rounded-3" style="width: 3rem; height: 3rem;">
