                    </div>
                    <div class="ms-4">
                        <h3 class="h5 mb-2">Submit Ideas</h3>
                        <p class="text-muted">Share your innovative ideas to improve your local community.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col">
                <div class="d-flex">
                    <div class="flex-shrink-0">
                        <div class="d-flex align-items-center justify-content-center bg-primary rounded-3" style="width: 3rem; height: 3rem;">
                            <svg class="text-white" width="24" height="24" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" aria-hidden="true">
                                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M16.5 10.5V6.75a4.5 4.5 0 10-9 0v3.75m-.75 11.25h10.5a2.25 2.25 0 002.25-2.25v-6.75a2.25 2.25 0 00-2.25-2.25H6.75a2.25 2.25 0 00-2.25 2.25v6.75a2.25 2.25 0 002.25 2.25z" />
                            </svg>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="ms-4">
                        <h3 class="h5 mb-2">Collaborate</h3>
                        <p class="text-muted">Work together with other community members to refine and improve ideas.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col">
                <div class="d-flex">
                    <div class="flex-shrink-0">
                        <div class="d-flex align-items-center justify-content-center bg-primary rounded-3" style="width: 3rem; height: 3rem;">
                            <svg class="text-white" width="24" height="24" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" aria-hidden="true">
                                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M16.023 9.348h4.992v-.001M2.985 19.644v-4.992m0 0h4.992m-4.993 0l3.181 3.183a8.25 8.25 0 0013.803-3.7M4.031 9.865a8.25 8.25 0 0113.803-3.7l3.181 3.182m0-4.991v4.99" />
                            </svg>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="ms-4">
                        <h3 class="h5 mb-2">Track Progress</h3>
                        <p class="text-muted">Follow the implementation of community-approved suggestions and see real change happen.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col">
                <div class="d-flex">
                    <div class="flex-shrink-0">
                        <div class="d-flex align-items-center justify-content-center bg-primary rounded-3" style="width: 3rem; height: 3rem;">
                            <svg class="text-white" width="24" height="24" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" aria-hidden="true">
                                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M7.864 4.243A7.5 7.5 0 0119.5 10.5c0 2.92-.556 5.709-1.568 8.268M5.742 6.364A7.465 7.465 0 004.5 10.5a7.464 7.464 0 01-1.15 3.993m1.989 3.559A11.209 11.209 0 008.25 10.5a3.75 3.75 0 117.5 0c0 .527-.021 1.049-.064 1.565M12 10.5a14.94 14.94 0 01-3.6 9.75m6.633-4.596a18.666 18.666 0 01-2.485 5.33" />
                            </svg>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="ms-4">
                        <h3 class="h5 mb-2">Make an Impact</h3>
                        <p class="text-muted">Be part of the positive change in your town and see your ideas come to life.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>